item.description:
Friends,

Healthbox is organizing an open house at its Kendall Square office on Feb 1. This is a tremendous opportunity to network with the people behind one of the top startup accelerators focused on health IT. Also a unique chance to see the inner workings of an accelerator. You will also get to meet the startups who graduated from Healthbox Boston 2012 program, along with several leading VCs, angels and Healthbox mentors.

Please feel free to contact me at sahil@healthbox.com for any questions.

Thanks,
Sahil
item.name: Healthbox Boston open house
